[[["det", "nmod", "case"], "The Cost of Gratefulness."], [["advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "cop", "case", "nsubj", "nmod:poss", "advmod", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "amod", "nmod", "case"], "When I was about thirteen, my father frequently took me on short outings on Saturdays."], [["nmod", "case", "det", "compound", "nmod", "case", "det", "nsubj", "advmod", "nmod", "case", "amod", "compound", "compound"], "On the way home from these trips, we often stopped for ten-cent ice cream cones."], [["nsubj", "xcomp", "cop", "ccomp", "nsubj", "nmod:poss", "aux", "nmod", "case", "det", "compound", "compound", "cc", "conj", "advcl", "nmod", "case", "det", "nsubj", "xcomp", "dobj", "nsubj", "aux", "cc", "conj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj"], "I couldnt be sure my father would stop at the ice cream store, but from the time we started heading home, I would hope and pray that he would."], [["nsubj", "ccomp", "nsubj", "aux", "cc:preconj", "advmod", "nmod", "case", "det", "compound", "compound", "cc", "conj", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "compound"], "I knew we would either go straight for the ice cream store or turn and go home empty-handed."], [["nsubj", "aux", "xcomp", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "compound", "compound", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "aux", "ccomp", "nsubj", "xcomp", "dep", "nsubj", "compound", "advmod", "dobj", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "xcomp"], "He would ask, Would you like an ice cream cone and I would say, That sounds great, Dad! Id always have chocolate and hed have vanilla."], [["nsubj", "aux", "iobj", "dobj", "nummod", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "aux", "compound:prt", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "nmod:poss"], "He would hand me twenty cents and I would run in to buy our cones."], [["nsubj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det"], "Wed eat them in the car."], [["nsubj", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "dobj", "compound", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "cop"], "I loved my dad and I loved ice creamXso this was heaven."], [["nmod:tmod", "nummod", "amod", "nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "aux", "cc", "conj", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss"], "One fateful day we were heading home, and I was hoping and praying for the beautiful sound of his offer."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "dep", "aux", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "compound", "compound", "nmod:tmod"], "Then it came, Would you like an ice cream cone today?"], [["cc", "advmod", "nsubj", "parataxis", "nsubj", "xcomp", "nmod", "case", "advmod", "advmod"], "But then he said, It sounds good to me too, Son."], [["advmod", "aux", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "nmod:tmod"], "How would you like to treat today?"], [["nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "compound", "cop"], "I could afford it, but saving money was important."], [["nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "xcomp", "nsubj"], "Dad had often told me that."], [["cc", "advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "amod", "nsubj", "compound", "amod", "advmod", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "compound:prt"], "And when it came to my own money, ice cream just didnt seem like a good thing to spend it on."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "dep", "nmod", "case", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "cop", "det", "amod", "acl", "mark", "dobj", "compound:prt", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "amod", "advmod"], "Why didnt it occur to me that this was a golden opportunity to give something back to my very generous father?"], [["advmod", "dep", "nsubj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "amod", "dep", "compound", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "aux", "neg", "iobj", "dobj", "det", "amod"], "Why didnt I think that he had bought me at least fifty cream cones, and I had never bought him a single one?"], [["cc", "nsubj", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "aux", "cop", "det", "acl", "mark", "dobj", "nummod"], "But all I could think was the idea of spending twenty cents!"], [["nmod", "case", "det", "nmod", "case", "amod", "amod", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "amod", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "aux", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "acl:relcl", "dep", "dep", "parataxis", "nmod", "case", "det", "nsubj", "ccomp", "nsubj"], "In a fit of selfish, miserly ingratitude, I said the awful words that have rung in my ears ever since: Well, in that case, I guess Ill pass."], [["nsubj", "nmod:poss", "advmod", "advmod", "dep", "xcomp"], "My father just said, All right, Son."], [["cc", "advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "nsubj", "ccomp", "advmod", "dep", "nsubj", "aux", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "xcomp", "mark", "advmod"], "But as we turned to head home, I realized how wrong I had been and begged him to turn back."], [["cc", "nsubj", "advmod", "ccomp", "nsubj", "acl:relcl", "discourse", "nsubj", "advmod", "dobj", "compound", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "xcomp", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss"], "But he just said, Thats OK. We dont really need ice cream, and he wouldnt listen to my pleading."], [["nsubj", "xcomp", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "cc", "conj"], "I felt awful about my selfishness and ungratefulness."], [["nsubj", "dep", "dobj", "nmod", "advmod", "cc", "conj", "advmod", "xcomp"], "He didnt rub it in, though, or even act disappointed."], [["nsubj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "ccomp", "nsubj", "nummod", "cc", "conj", "advmod", "advmod", "nmod:npmod", "det", "advcl", "dep", "advmod", "nsubj", "ccomp", "nmod", "case", "det", "nsubj", "aux", "aux", "iobj", "dobj", "nummod", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "aux", "aux", "cop", "det", "amod", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "compound", "advmod"], "I learned that generosity goes two ways and gratitude sometimes costs a little more than just thank you. On that day gratefulness would have cost me twenty cents, and it would have been the best ice cream Id ever had."], [["nsubj", "iobj", "dobj", "nummod", "amod"], "Ill tell you one more thing."], [["dep", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "det", "nmod:tmod", "det", "amod", "cc", "conj", "advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "amod", "nsubj", "advmod", "aux", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "compound", "compound", "nmod:tmod"], "We went on another trip the next week, and as we approached the crucial corner I said, Dad, would you like an ice cream cone today?"], [["nsubj", "nmod", "case", "compound", "appos", "det", "nmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "compound", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "compound", "conj", "compound", "compound", "cc", "conj", "compound"], "w by Randal Jones, The Cost of Gratefulness from Chicken Soup for the Teenage Soul, edited by Jack Canfield, Mark Victor Hansen, and Kimberly Kirberger."], [["nmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "compound", "appos", "compound"], "Reprinted with permission of Health Communications, Inc. www.hcibooks.com"]]